vernac_cmds: Lemma closed_wrt_modvars_switch: forall a sl n F, closed_wrt_modvars (Sswitch a sl) F -> closed_wrt_modvars (seq_of_labeled_statement (select_switch n sl)) F.
intros rho te' H0; apply H.
revert l Heqo s H0; induction sl ;intros.

revert s H; induction sl; simpl; intros; auto.
Lemma frame_tc_expr: forall {CS: compspecs} (Q F: mpred) Delta e rho, Q |-- tc_expr Delta e rho -> Q * F |-- tc_expr Delta e rho.
eapply derives_trans; [apply sepcon_derives; [apply H | apply derives_refl ] | ].
Lemma subp_trans': forall A (NA: ageable A) (P Q R: pred A) w, app_pred (P >=> Q) w -> app_pred (Q >=> R) w -> app_pred (P >=> R) w.
Lemma prop_subp: forall A (NA: ageable A) (P Q: Prop) (w: nat), (P -> Q) -> app_pred (!! P >=> !! Q) w.
Lemma andp_subp'_right: forall A (NA: ageable A) (P Q R: pred A) w, app_pred (P >=> Q) w -> app_pred (P >=> R) w -> app_pred (P >=> Q && R) w.
Lemma prop_true_imp: forall {A} {agA: ageable A} (P: Prop) (Q: pred A), P -> (!! P --> Q)%pred = Q.
Lemma prop_imp_right: forall A (agA: ageable A) (P: Prop) (Q R: pred A), (P -> (Q |-- R)) -> Q |-- !! P --> R.
Lemma imp_right: forall A (agA: ageable A) (P Q R : pred A), P && Q |-- R -> P |-- Q --> R.
Lemma prop_andp_subp': forall (A : Type) (agA : ageable A) (P : Prop) (S: pred nat) (Q R : pred A), (P -> S |-- Q >=> R)%pred -> (S |-- !! P && Q >=> R)%pred.
Lemma tc_expr_sound {CS: compspecs}: forall Delta e rho, typecheck_environ Delta rho -> tc_expr Delta e rho |-- !! tc_val (typeof e) (eval_expr e rho).
Lemma unfash_allp: forall {A} {agA: ageable A} {B} (f: B -> pred nat), @unfash _ agA (allp f) = allp (fun x:B => unfash (f x)).
Lemma fash_TT: forall {A} {agA: ageable A}, @unfash A agA TT = TT.
Lemma allp_andp: forall {A} {NA: ageable A} {B: Type} (b0: B) (P: B -> pred A) (Q: pred A), (allp P && Q = allp (fun x => P x && Q))%pred.
Lemma unfash_prop_imp: forall {A} {agA: ageable A} (P: Prop) (Q: pred nat), (@unfash _ agA (prop P --> Q) = prop P --> @unfash _ agA Q)%pred.
Lemma unfash_imp: forall {A} {NA: ageable A} (P Q: pred nat), (@unfash A _ (P --> Q) = (@unfash A _ P) --> @unfash A _ Q)%pred.
Lemma unfash_andp: forall {A} {agA: ageable A} (P Q: pred nat), (@unfash A agA (andp P Q) = andp (@unfash A agA P) (@unfash A agA Q)).
Lemma andp_imp_e: forall (A : Type) (agA : ageable A) (P Q : pred A), P && (P --> Q) |-- Q.
Lemma andp_imp_e': forall (A : Type) (agA : ageable A) (P Q : pred A), P && (P --> Q) |-- P && Q.

Lemma switch_rguard: forall (Espec : OracleKind) (R : ret_assert) (psi : genv) (F : assert) (Delta' : tycontext) (k : cont), rguard Espec psi Delta' (frame_ret_assert R F) k |-- (rguard Espec psi Delta' (frame_ret_assert (switch_ret_assert R) F) (Kswitch :: k)).
pose (ek' := match ek with | EK_normal => EK_normal | EK_break => EK_normal | EK_continue => EK_continue | EK_return => EK_return end).
pose (vl' := match ek with | EK_normal => None | EK_break => None | EK_continue => None | EK_return => vl end).
set (rho' := construct_rho (filter_genv psi) vx' tx') in *.
destruct R as [?R ?R ?R ?R]; destruct ek; subst ek' vl'; simpl; auto.
Lemma unfash_fash_imp: forall A (NA: ageable A) P Q, @unfash A _ (# (P --> Q)) |-- P --> Q.

Lemma assert_safe_step_nostore: forall {cs: compspecs} Espec psi vx vx2 tx tx2 k1 k2 Delta e rho, (forall jm jm', age1 jm = Some jm' -> app_pred (tc_expr Delta e rho) (m_phi jm) -> cl_step psi (State vx tx k1) (m_dry jm) (State vx2 tx2 k2) (m_dry jm)) -> assert_safe Espec psi vx2 tx2 k2 (construct_rho (filter_genv psi) vx2 tx2) && tc_expr Delta e rho |-- assert_safe Espec psi vx tx k1 (construct_rho (filter_genv psi) vx tx).
eexists; split; eauto; eexists; repeat split; eauto.
eapply pred_hereditary in Hw; [ | instantiate (1:= (m_phi jm')); apply age_jm_phi; auto].

Lemma semax_switch: forall {CS: compspecs} Espec Delta (Q: assert) a sl R, is_int_type (typeof a) = true -> (forall rho, Q rho |-- tc_expr Delta a rho) -> (forall n, semax Espec Delta (fun rho => andp (prop (eval_expr a rho = Vint n)) (Q rho)) (seq_of_labeled_statement (select_switch (Int.unsigned n) sl)) (switch_ret_assert R)) -> semax Espec Delta Q (Sswitch a sl) R.
rewrite <- andp_assoc; rewrite (andp_comm (believe _ _ _ _)); rewrite andp_assoc; apply prop_andp_left; intro.
set (rho := construct_rho (filter_genv psi) vx tx) in *.
apply frame_tc_expr with (F0 := F rho) in H0.
destruct (eval_expr a rho) as [ | n | | | |] eqn:?; try contradiction H0'.

rewrite prop_true_andp by (eapply closed_wrt_modvars_switch with (n:= Int.unsigned n); eauto).
forget (funassert Delta' rho && (F rho * Q rho))%pred as FQ.
eapply typecheck_environ_sub in H4; try eassumption.
